original_title: Archangel from the Winter's End Chronicles: Episode III - Deadliest of the Species
overview: The fight against the forces of the Legion continues in Episode III - Deadliest of the Species. Archangel must rescue his son Jon, who has been taken prisoner by the evil skyraider, Mordecai Judd. Aboard the flagship of Jasmin Synn, Supreme Warlord of London, the battle will be determined.
title: Archangel from the Winter's End Chronicles: Episode III - Deadliest of the Species
